#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:2 e5cd1839547b479da591b60f2de71e22
msgid "安信可 2.4G系列模块 FAQ"
msgstr "Ai-Thinker 2.4G Series Module FAQ"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:18 51cada1560ba47dd9b9e7bcae05aca18
msgid "Si24R1芯片与nRF24L01+芯片有什么区别?"
msgstr "What is the difference between the Si24R1 chip and the nRF24L01+ chip?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:19 33c4f0c6adf3416ca919caab1c872f22
msgid "Si24R1芯片与nRF24L01+芯片兼容，可以直接替换。SI24R1芯片的优点就是SHDN关断状态的电流要小，standby-I状态的电流也要小，同时SI24R1芯片支持更大功率的输出7dBm，（需要软件设置内部寄存器配置使之工作在7dBm模式），SI24R1的总的平均电流消耗要比nRF24L01+的小。"
msgstr "The Si24R1 chip is compatible with the nRF24L01+ chip and can be used as a direct replacement. The advantages of the Si24R1 chip are lower current consumption in SHDN shutdown state and lower current consumption in standby-I state. At the same time, the Si24R1 chip supports a higher output power of 7dBm. (Software configuration of internal registers is required to make it work in 7dBm mode. ) The overall average current consumption of the Si24R1 is lower than that of the nRF24L01+."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:22 437f33c9beee4494beb6193c3abc0627
msgid "Si24R1与nRF24L01+与BK2425芯片哪一个性能比较好?"
msgstr "Which chip has better performance: Si24R1, nRF24L01+, or BK2425?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:24 9377bef18f92487eb068a4184cc744a3
msgid "答：从功率上比较：Si24R1最大功率是5mV>BK2425最大功率是2.5mV>nRF24L01最大功率是1mV"
msgstr "A: In terms of power: Si24R1 maximum power is 5mV > BK2425 maximum power is 2.5mV > nRF24L01 maximum power is 1mV."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:27 3d0bc3587bdf41b1b4f323e419b2731a
msgid "NF-03跟24l01兼容吗"
msgstr "Is NF-03 compatible with 24L01?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:29 38eb78f9524342259096b8e9f6473eb7
msgid "兼容，支持多发一收"
msgstr "Compatible. It supports multiple transmitters and one receiver."

