msgstr "Yes, they can communicate."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:69 681be70becf1458b94d98d2a44c575c4
msgid "\"NF-04多少米"
msgstr "How far is the NF-04 transmission distance?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:73 99ca7d0ca6a849c0a38e24effbfdb613
msgid "怎么区分NF-01-N和NF-01-S"
msgstr "How to distinguish NF-01-N and NF-01-S?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:74 bce8d92610f349eb902d18ad7df39383
msgid "他们使用的射频芯片不一样 可以参考芯片手册"
msgstr "They use different RF chips. You can refer to the chip manuals."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:77 f4cce3f5c3014eaaa6868080e7f6a600
msgid "这种3.3V供电的2.4G  NF-04-MI模块，能否与5V供电的单片机信号线直接连接"
msgstr "Can this 3.3V-powered 2.4G NF-04-MI module be directly connected to the signal lines of a 5V-powered MCU?"

