#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:81 740711c5bd2b48e18c14dd134ec5c893
msgid "NF-03模块有没有程序的"
msgstr "Does the NF-03 module come with a program?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:82 a1d0d11a647843b5b5d2859c3904f97e
msgid "NF-03这款是射频芯片，所以不带程序的，通过MCU寄存器去操作"
msgstr "NF-03 is an RF chip, so it does not come with a program. It is operated by MCU register configuration."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:85 c1e78d8047b240bbaa44b85e4c13ed83
msgid "NF-01-S 这个是wifi透传吗?是走wifi协议吗?"
msgstr "Is NF-01-S Wi-Fi transparent transmission? Does it use the Wi-Fi protocol?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:86 487f1de4924f444083f8e991adca3e19
msgid "支持SPI透传,走的不是WIFI协议 ,是SPI协议"
msgstr "It supports SPI transparent transmission. It does not use the Wi-Fi protocol; it uses the SPI protocol."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:89 4fa97d1eabd04edaa626265e9750ff2e
msgid "NF-01-S可以做AP吗。 设备跟你们的模块连，手机APP跟模块连。实现透传。"
msgstr "Can NF-01-S work as an AP? Devices connect to the module, and the mobile app connects to the module to implement transparent transmission."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:91 f4d06c26277746ff8cddf7fe758e6d19
msgid "SPI协议，这个只是纯射频模块，没有AP这种概念哦"
msgstr "It uses the SPI protocol. This is only a pure RF module, so there is no AP concept."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:94 b8514c2379374bd3912a3a67855b99ee
msgid "2.4G系列有5V供电的吗"
msgstr "Are there any 5V-powered modules in the 2.4G series?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:95 eacb9ae73bbc4ea0b96990bd1e1688c4
msgid "2.4G模块都是3.3V供电的，如果使用5V供电请自行设计电路进行降压"
msgstr "All 2.4G modules are powered by 3.3V. If using a 5V power supply, please design your own step-down circuit."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:98 7567ca779fac49699aa3181ee03c52f9
msgid "\"有串口通信的2.4G模块吗"
msgstr "Are there 2.4G modules with serial communication?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:99 3a0d35806b8145e1b1d935b2ea5a4a89
msgid "没有，2.4g都是SPI通信的，是单2.4，不是WIFI"
msgstr "No. All 2.4G modules use SPI communication. They are single 2.4G modules, not Wi-Fi modules."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:102 6eb111b9c8f94ab7bcd7ea5d22376281
msgid "Nf-02可以做音频传输吧？"
