#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:103 62b9221a7f5d49de86489b499e0a2a07
msgid "不行哦"
msgstr "No."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:106 87b43e6f0b3e414883507569bb5bb7ec
msgid "为什么叫邦定2401模块？与普通的2401模块有什么不同？"
msgstr "Why is it called a bonded 2401 module? What is the difference from an ordinary 2401 module?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:107 787aa67adaa94779917f05514076a842
msgid "使用的射频芯片不一样"
msgstr "The RF chip used is different."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:110 b1054be6d20d41daa5b88bb3b909c61a
msgid "NF-02是发射器吧？接收呢"
