msgstr "Which modules can be used as receivers for the NF-02 module?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:115 7733e9f5c7994273af5b5426c079cdf8
msgid "发送和接收都可以用这个，2.4G属于收发模块"
msgstr "This module can be used for both transmitting and receiving. 2.4G modules are transceiver modules."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:119 1aff3b629b7141be9ae8a18fe96113d5
msgid "\"NF-02   和 NF-03  在数据在 能对接的吧？ 能不有 NF-02 做一款 跟NF-03一样的接口？"
msgstr "Can NF-02 and NF-03 connect with each other in terms of data? Can you make an NF-02 with the same interface as NF-03?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:121 888e727cda5840358199ae69efc937e7
msgid "数据可以对接的，但是我们没有跟NF-03一样接口的NF-02"
msgstr "The data can connect with each other, but we do not have an NF-02 with the same interface as NF-03."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:124 3a8d4ff84e2e438fb1c3bf5502806ed3
msgid "能做遥控的是那种"
msgstr "Which module can be used for remote control?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:126 d6a9c280ddf14177a78508cf429eeeb0
msgid "2.4G、WIFI都可以"
msgstr "Both 2.4G and Wi-Fi can be used."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:130 615655a0190140eebea6a17c9b8f3a57
msgid "这款2.4G  NF-03模块实际使用过程中，最大的发射功率可以配置成多少啊？"
msgstr "In actual use, what is the maximum transmit power that this 2.4G NF-03 module can be configured to?"

