msgid "7dbm，您可以查看我们官网的芯片手册"
msgstr "7dBm. You can check the chip manual on our official website."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:134 1435895cfbb5495ba9f52547a96c9ad9
msgid "NF-04-MI模块需要自己往模块的芯片里面编写程序吗？"
msgstr "Do I need to write programs into the chip of the NF-04-MI module myself?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:136 da8271518a73484d96e2fc67be7b0928
