msgid "不会有干扰的"
msgstr "No, there will be no interference."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:143 00a85c208a8c473aba603c26f6933361
msgid "这个NF-03是串口透传的吗？ 有多少个信道？"
msgstr "Is this NF-03 a serial transparent transmission module? How many channels does it have?"

