msgid "不是串口透传哦,信道您可以查看芯片手册哈"
msgstr "It is not serial transparent transmission. For channels, you can refer to the chip manual."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:148 d1057e5a978249c49cb7e14cce2f558a
msgid "是否可以将SI24R1连接至电脑并显示接受的数据？是不是有配套的硬件模块？"
msgstr "Can Si24R1 be connected to a computer and display received data? Is there a supporting hardware module?"

