msgid "SI24R1模块是需要MCU去驱动才能进行使用"
msgstr "The Si24R1 module requires an MCU to drive it before it can be used."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:152 3c06162969c447a3a7435b53b09ec07c
msgid "NF-03模块是免开发模块，还是一定要连接mcu，如果用这个模块连接RC522射频模块，可以正常工作吗"
msgstr "Is the NF-03 module a development-free module, or must it be connected to an MCU? If this module is connected to an RC522 RF module, can it work properly?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:153 15a5bf344784432286274b960967a9ca
msgid "一定要接MCU"
msgstr "It must be connected to an MCU."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:156 5f408c9691a746d9b8ea8ab8184c5243
msgid "2.4G模块 你们提供上位机端的测试工具吗？ 如果我使用你们的模块 那应该怎样测试这个模块的工作情况呢"
msgstr "Do you provide a PC-side test tool for 2.4G modules? If I use your module, how should I test whether the module is working properly?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:158 0082b565f18a4121a1c6c71ace4e4dd7
msgid "我们没有上位机端的测试工具，无法提供,通过MCU驱动."
msgstr "We do not have a PC-side test tool and cannot provide one. It is driven through an MCU."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:162 6056d3bcaf244537a3031fc832a518e7
msgid "NF-04-MI可以直接连串口透传吗？"
msgstr "Can NF-04-MI be directly connected to a serial port for transparent transmission?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:164 82dc46b86a684684bbde2f3a59883256
msgid "不可以"
msgstr "No."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:167 5640b6b1391f4fe18d3e0d72f92cfd12
msgid "NF-02延时时间是多久"
msgstr "What is the delay time of NF-02?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:168 b25620109be84b99b00b9f20d84126b8
msgid "200ms"
msgstr "200ms."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:171 58f4039eeb8e43b291b5f495bc68f805
msgid "Nf-03这个程序和NRF24L01的通用吗"
msgstr "Is the program for NF-03 compatible with NRF24L01?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:172 6261bea33b4246f3801008d075060b42
msgid "通用"
msgstr "Yes, compatible."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:176 682a434a59d64c8bb8f44baed5e046ab
msgid "NF-04-MI手册上说能传输120米，实际测试10米不到，有办法提高通讯距离吗 ？如果布线好的话，能传输多远呢，速度最低的情况下，你们测试试过吗"
msgstr "The NF-04-MI manual says it can transmit 120 meters, but the actual test is less than 10 meters. Is there any way to improve the communication distance? If the wiring is good, how far can it transmit? Have you tested it at the lowest speed?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:178 323cbc4a78ff408697f0c7666f7b1e38
msgid "改善天线区域的布线。NF-04-MI这个不能传远距离的，如果需要传远距离推荐使用NF-03，NF-03能传输175米，NF-04-MI只能传30米"
msgstr "Improve the wiring in the antenna area. NF-04-MI is not suitable for long-distance transmission. If long-distance transmission is required, NF-03 is recommended. NF-03 can transmit 175 meters, while NF-04-MI can only transmit 30 meters."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:181 1d596905e2484f94a261b21f8abc9291
msgid "nrf24L01可以和BK2425通讯对吧"
msgstr "Can nRF24L01 communicate with BK2425?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:183 ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:236 ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:241 030b5bc439b0475986859a275d24a9a7 0ff542276de8413c9469da18ba39758d 110d73b9512442d88ad80aacb9ce128e
msgid "可以的"
msgstr "Yes."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:186 3ae7b15435714b54b8b9eea9dc2b32b2
msgid "NF-03，想改用ipx胶棒天线，要怎么焊接？"
msgstr "For NF-03, if I want to use an IPEX rubber antenna instead, how should I solder it?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:187 829b4edb418c4f3193902fbed5bff77c
msgid "这个无法改用哦，上面没有预留IPEX接口，只能使用板载天线"
msgstr "This cannot be changed. There is no reserved IPEX interface on it, so only the onboard antenna can be used."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:190 31cf38c2d2284e3f81cf713d25dcf082
msgid "2.4G模块是烧录好程序的吗？透传使用"
msgstr "Are 2.4G modules pre-programmed? Can they be used for transparent transmission?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:191 2e13a4dbb41048069e14d12de02b45ac
msgid "不能透传，NF-03只是一个射频模块，程序是已经固化好的"
msgstr "They cannot be used for transparent transmission. NF-03 is only an RF module, and the program is already solidified."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:194 44e7f3cea1284c488b1ef6ec3fbed2b5
msgid "NF-02-PA要不要焊电容？"
msgstr "Does NF-02-PA require soldering a capacitor?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/2.4G/index.rst:195 7c2a682c3e2f4becb0d3c860427b0e91
msgid "不需要焊电容"
msgstr "No capacitor needs to be soldered."

